      <title>NVIDIA在收益下降后，亚洲芯片股票下跌，前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/asian-chip-shares-drop-after-nvidia-tumbles-on-earnings-outlook-m7o3c4k4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在NVIDIA Corp.的收入未能给投资者留下深刻印象，并使股票在美国交易中投掷后，亚洲与筹码相关的股票沉没了。]]></description>
